item.title: Bobby Hebb - Sunny - Ukulele Cheats
item.description: Play along video for the song Sunny by Bobby Hebb from the channel Ukulele Cheats. Chords used in the song: A7, A♯maj7, Dm, Dm6, Dm7, Dmadd5, D♯9, Em7, Esus4, F9.

item.title: Audrey Hepburn - Moon River - Ukulele Cheats
item.description: Play along video for the song Moon River by Audrey Hepburn from the channel Ukulele Cheats. Chords used in the song: A7, Am7, A♯, A♯m6, B7, Bm, Bm6, C7, C♯7, D, D7, Dm, Dm6, D♯, E7, Em, Em6, Em7, F, F7, F♯7, F♯m7, G, G7, Gm, Gm6.
